I see that this logic was in the old code but CARDINALITY_SINGE_SCORE and CARDINALITY_OTHER_SCORE are both always equal to 1000, so maybe it should be combined into a single constant like CARDINALITY_SCORE?
If so, the code can be simplified to:
if(index.isCompositeIndex()){
    return CARDINALITY_SINGE_SCORE;
}
return 0.0;

